Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.01,0:02:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多想確認的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.05,0:02:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拇指姑娘的故事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我 是演什麼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想扮演什麼角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.03,0:02:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以自己決定麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就跟你決定自己的活法是一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這個故事沒有角色分配的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這個故事裡 本來就沒有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得自己來想來決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那種準備都沒做好就闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪想得到會出這檔子事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底我都不知道自己會把身體借出去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你還為什麼要挺身來這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…一時衝動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連能不能回去也不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回不去了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好辦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事也是有可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回不去我會怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保持這種狀態會不會很糟糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定自己的角色麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正 我基本上是個樂觀主義者所以也沒啥大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就很介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 真沒真沒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說有始必有終啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有不會停的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.97,0:03:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要人還活著雨就總會停的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是要看店長的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你稀里糊塗的就真會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就回不去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路的是店長的丈夫才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒動搖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想讓店長轉向我這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓她笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 要脫多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部脫光？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都沒計劃性的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 只要後背就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半身就這樣直接去泡澡麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會變得濕漉漉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也知道我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還能張得了口讓我做這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 把這件事忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把衣服穿上 拒絕我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼才拒絕得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會先進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之後過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要跟我一起洗麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定 小六花也挺願意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在某時某地跟葉月君進展不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心裡也還是會無意識地期待這種事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後背變的好柔軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這麼白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不煉出點肌肉來可不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啊 後背很髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能髒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有動物的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡撫摸你的後背
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這活著的聲音從你身後傳過來 毫無防備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人安心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經把新的後背…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡 還是做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我消失了的話事情就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想在你身邊多呆一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一點沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然變心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然都喜歡上了 就得承認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然總有一天會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算多麼不像樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.65,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果王子不回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你準備怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.77,0:07:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 難道那樣的話就只有我一個人出局麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能允許這種悲劇發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是王子的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 之前好不容易才把店長帶到遊樂園去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是純真無邪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘不了島尾君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼那麼喜歡店長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼為她著想到這種程度呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡她什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契機呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契機？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始 我只是覺得這個初中男生背挺得真直啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 說實話是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊 發生了點事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看的話就偶然發現她澆水時手邊出現了彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她沉浸在那道光裡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得她真像個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是視線就沒法從她身上移開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對她的第一印象是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可稍微瞭解一下的話就覺得她也很有大人樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又很有店長的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走過她身邊總能聞到土壤的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讓我覺得…只是覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然 很喜歡她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.17,0:09:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拇指公主接下來就HE了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被青蛙擄走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被金龜子搶去當新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還被老鼠婆婆照顧什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是燕子的翅膀痊癒之後還是會去花田里見王子麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子的腦子秀逗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想完成這個故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就 趕緊回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我先引誘你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.80,0:09:46.52,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得對不起我麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你結果還是在想著順其自然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從一開始這就只是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心拒絕什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一次都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再這樣用死去的丈夫做擋箭牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…要怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是轉移下注意力比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:05.08,setting,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz18.809\pos(157,130)}今 天 的 推 薦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推薦什麼的 我還真是不擅長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先把價格適中的花按顏色和大小分好類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後讓客人從中自由選擇主花材再做成花束就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不難吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是勉強去跟人推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而還會讓對方覺得你不擅長到時候起反效果哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是這麼說 不過總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是不討厭向客人推薦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照當天的天氣和心情適當地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給那些不知道選擇什麼花的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供一個契機就好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你太正經了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.37,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然察言觀色也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能太過於糾結別人的臉色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你不來做決定的話客人也會困擾的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用那麼拐彎抹角的說法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想過幫葉月修剪頭髮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 只是想摸摸他的後背
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得自己決定自己到底想怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…燈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是忘了關了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷藏櫃OK
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫃檯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 我忘了關抽屜麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近做事還真是馬虎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主鎮守著沉澱的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盆栽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防腐劑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不管怎麼拔還是不見少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.84,0:13:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期天一大早就找你過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一角完事了之後就休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越有夏天的感覺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想趁著涼快的時候趕快完事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊都是我拉著你給店裡幫忙耽誤了時間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是自己嫌麻煩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可放著不管的話它們又會一頓瘋長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美惠姐你家有院子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這院子小得可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠寬敞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 我做了紫蘇汁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自製的 很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少放糖 多放檸檬酸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都長得比我還高了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過幾天 我想在這裡種上薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 長長的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就像愛麗絲夢遊仙境裡的迷宮一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼又來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君你的少女興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女情結讓人起雞皮疙瘩 我挺喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼讓人起雞皮疙瘩你這是人身攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這想法本來就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是命薄如紙也要戀愛的少女？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種裝脆弱的行為才讓人受不了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是裝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是單純地很喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倩女命薄亦逢戀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一腔熱血尚暖時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何懼明朝日月淺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君修剪造型很勤快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很擅長栽培大朵的薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這陣子 花數多了好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.72,0:15:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這種小朵的薔薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是我喜歡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花朵有時候太能說會道也讓人傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有主人的夏天的院子就更是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很忙麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說忙也沒什麼 我反正只要在家工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也有工作要做的 一直讓你幫忙真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.93,0:15:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去店裡正好能解決我運動不足 正合適哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能這麼說真讓我安心不少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你是不是工作上太努力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有休息麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:15:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就相當於休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不就只是來讓我差遣的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有其他的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正工作也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我獨身沒資格說這話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不適合做寡婦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花你一個人攬了太多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說啊 老顧客中有沒有年輕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了突然間？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天附近的圖書館下午1點就要關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候正好去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果汁很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.90,0:16:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得收拾下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺各種被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 說我不適合做寡婦什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能讓我來選薔薇呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島尾君種的薔薇 漂亮的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是沒有死心麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使說我必須往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算在你心裡一輩子都第二也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心拒絕什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一次都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明也知道我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還能張得了口讓我做這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 比如說和我來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談次婚外戀怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會比店長您活得更長哦 雖然有點對不住您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就算您說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.08,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不轉過頭來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.06,0:18:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就大喊大叫了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次休假的時候能去麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.01,SETTING2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.592\pos(126,62)}入園招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.01,SETTING3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.095\pos(160,113)}1張僅限一位使用（4歲以下兒童免費）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:30.01,setting,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.029\pos(187,150)}有效期限不限  非賣品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從宣傳的人那裡拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再這樣用死去的丈夫做擋箭牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.18,0:18:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我讓他背過身去的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽一個年紀比我小的人說了些好聽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有點輕飄飄的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就覺得反正他還年輕經得起折騰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:56.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人魚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就傷害了他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟個笨蛋似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館內禁止私語
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,館內請不要大聲喧嘩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 那個很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個量的確會讓人以為你是要搞暑假自由研究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只和我先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只和我先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先生…是我的初戀…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說真正談過戀愛的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有島尾君一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.68,0:20:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說和島尾君那時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來也是我先單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到了這種年紀還會有人喜歡上我什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也從來沒想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.91,0:20:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡葉月君你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:30.99,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも夢の中では あなたは笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:30.99,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢中的你永遠是笑著的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:38.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしてね 消えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.99,0:21:38.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不會消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.66,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I care you everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.66,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關心你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You care me everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:42.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你關心我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.96,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっといつまででも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:45.96,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是永久的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.35,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:47.35,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:49.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still my everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:49.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:52.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛してるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:52.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:58.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏に降った 雪のような
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:58.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正如盛夏裡飄落的雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:04.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは儚い奇跡なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.91,0:22:04.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個易碎的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:06.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我為何是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:11.73,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会わなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:11.73,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒有遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:18.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こんなに切なくて 胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:18.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心也不會如此絞痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.51,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,こともなかったそれでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.51,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:28.20,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたに出会えなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:28.20,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是沒能遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:35.06,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強さも優しさも 知らずにいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:35.06,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就無法領悟強大與溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:44.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じればすぐそこに あなたがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:44.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼你就在離我那麼近的地方
